column5: Color matching function (Stiles & Burch 1959 10-deg RGB) from the Colour and Vision Research Laboratory (http://cvrl.ioo.ucl.ac.uk/). Normalized to a maximum value of 1 and normalized for luminance using the equation L = SQRT(0.241*R^2 + 0.691*G^2 + 0.068*B^2) from http://alienryderflex.com/hsp.html
